HEADWORD: Bartizan
<hw>Bar"ti*zan`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf.
<er>Brettice</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Arch.)</fld> <def>A small, overhanging
